description: Quickly export threads.net user's follower and following lists as downloadable CSVs with just one click using this convenient… Followers Exporter for Threads is a handy Chrome extension that allows you to easily export the followers and followings of any Threads user. To use it, simply click on the extension icon and enter the username of the Threads.net user whose followers you want to export. To export followings, enter the username and toggle the "Followers / Followings" switch before starting the extraction. The extension will then fetch all of that user's data. Once the extraction is complete, click "Export Followers" and the data will be exported to a CSV file.The exported CSV contains useful information about each user, including the pk, username, full name, profile info, profile picture, verification status, follower count, and the time of data extraction.Extraction starts right after you make a request, so you get the data quickly. Duration varies based on the number of users to extract. Your data stays private and secure - it remains only on your device and is not stored or transmitted to any external servers. Note: Some users' personal configurations may result in fewer than 100 data items being exportable.Data PrivacyYour data stays on your device and is not stored or transmitted to our servers. We prioritize keeping your information secure and confidential.

description: TrackingTime è una applicazione collaborativa, basata su cloud che permette di gestire i tuoi compiti, di tracciare i tempi di… Time Tracking App that helps companies manage their projects, track working times and measure productivity.Available on PlayStore:https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.trackingtimeThe core of the app is a simple yet powerful task manager that allows you to stay organised while effortlessly keeping track of your working hours in real time. Because the app also focuses on collaboration, you’ll be able to organise your clients, projects and tasks on your dashboard while seeing the work being done by others on your team – with real-time updates, comments and notifications also built in. Additionally, you’ll never have to write out a timesheet again, as TrackingTime creates in-depth time analytics and performance reports automatically.Top FeaturesTasks Tracking:Keep track of your working times right from your to-do list with just one click. No need to fill out timesheets or set up timers.Built-in Collaboration Organise your team, projects and tasks. Real-time updates and notifications ensure everyone is always on the same page.Task Comments:Keep all the conversations about your tasks in one place.Subtasks:Break complex tasks into smaller achievable goals.Time and Performance Analytics:Building great projects, teams and companies takes time. Our detailed timesheets and performance reports show you exactly how much.International:TrackingTime is designed for global teams. The system is localised for Englisch, German and Spanish. More languages coming soon!Enterprise class Security:Our backend is built on top of Java Enterprise solutions, the same technology used by banks and top e-commerce providers.Top Benefits:Allows you to accurately measure employee productivityAllows for more flexible working conditions like remote working Brings more transparency into your daily business Helps you improve project budgeting and make better estimates Helps foster a culture of autonomy and openness Builds trust between your company and outsourced contractors Who is it for?:TrackingTime is designed for founders, project managers and freelancers who want to make the most out of their time. Most of our customers are small and medium sized businesses from creative industries such as web design, software development, news and media, PR and marketing, photography, architecture, digital arts, etc. Any knowledge worker can benefit from our service. Pricing:The current version of TrackingTime is completely free for teams up to 3 people. And the best part is: time tracking and collaboration features will always remain free! We are working on some great premium features (third party integrations and powerful analytics) that will improve the TrackingTime experience.For more information on TrackingTime, please visit our website at: www.trackingtime.co.

Crea un ambiente più inclusivo per i tuoi studenti.2)Per lavoroChe tu stia conducendo una riunione, ospitando un workshop o formando il tuo team, assicurati di renderlo produttivo, inclusivo e divertente.può essere utilizzato anche per giochi rompighiaccio, sessioni di brainstorming, team building.➤ Quali tipi supportiamo🔹Scelta multiplaTipo di sondaggio versatile per rompere il ghiaccio, prendere decisioni collettive e acquisire feedback sui voti. Mantieni il tuo pubblico coinvolto visualizzando i risultati del sondaggio in tempo reale sotto forma di grafici visivamente accattivanti.🔹Nuvola di paroleVisualizza le risposte più popolari in una bellissima nuvola di parole. Più volte viene usata una parola, più diventa grande. Le nuvole di parole sono ottimi spunti di conversazione ideali per invii di una sola parola.🔹QuizCrea un quiz dal vivo con un timer e una classifica e metti alla prova le conoscenze delle persone in modo divertente e interattivo.🔹Sondaggio di valutazioneScegli tra tre diverse scale di valutazione: icona, numerica e trascinabile per acquisire feedback immediato dai tuoi partecipanti. Esegui rapidi sondaggi sul polso e ottieni risultati in tempo reale con punteggi medi.🔹Apri testoConsenti ai partecipanti di digitare la propria risposta o commento. I sondaggi a testo aperto sono ottimi per sondaggi di feedback e sessioni di formazione o come strumento di collaborazione in piccole riunioni.🔹Sondaggio sulla classificaChiedi alle persone di dare priorità ai diversi elementi in base alla loro importanza. Un sondaggio di classificazione può aiutarti a identificare gli argomenti, i progetti o le aree più rilevanti e a prendere decisioni migliori.Supporteremo tipi di sondaggi, domande e risposte, ruota girevole, domande trivia, ruota girevole, ruota sì o no, concorsi a premi istantanei.Infine, puoi visualizzare ed esportare le tue domande o i risultati delle votazioni o dei quiz per ulteriori analisi.Live Polls Maker è un'app popolare sul Webstore Google Chorme. Altre app includono JustCall, Crunchbase, EmailDrop, Highspot, ProspectIn, AuthoredUp. ➤ Informativa sulla privacyI tuoi dati non vengono condivisi con nessuno, incluso il proprietario del componente aggiuntivo.Rispettiamo le leggi sulla privacy (in particolare GDPR e California Privacy Act) per proteggere i tuoi dati.
name: Creatore di sondaggi dal vivo

description: Visualizza le risposte di ChatGPT con i risultati di ricerca. Funziona su Google, Bing, ecc. Supporta GPT-4 e la funzione di… Scoprite l'inedito connubio tra i risultati di ricerca tradizionali e le risposte di chat generate dall'intelligenza artificiale con ChitChat, un'estensione per il browser che potenzia le capacità dei motori di ricerca. L'estensione, realizzata da ChatGPT, funziona perfettamente con Google, Bing, Yahoo e DuckDuckGo, presentando risposte generate dall'intelligenza artificiale accanto ai risultati di ricerca standard.Siete interessati ad avviare una conversazione con l'intelligenza artificiale subito dopo aver ottenuto la risposta? Con ChitChat, supportato dall'intelligenza di ChatGPT, è un gioco da ragazzi. Inoltre, con ChitChat per Chrome, è possibile accedere rapidamente all'estensione ChatGPT attraverso una finestra popup.Questo strumento gratuito combina le funzionalità avanzate di ChatGPT con la comodità del vostro browser web. Ponete qualsiasi domanda e ricevete risposte precise e concise in tempo reale, grazie alla potenza di ChatGPT. Migliorate la vostra esperienza di intelligenza artificiale con questa estensione per Chrome.Ecco una breve panoramica delle caratteristiche distintive di questa estensione:Accesso al browser Chrome: Con ChitChat, ChatGPT è facilmente accessibile dal popup dell'estensione del browser. Non è necessario passare a un sito web o a un'applicazione separata.Evidenziazione del codice: Questa funzione, utilizzando la comprensione intelligente di ChatGPT, identifica ed evidenzia i frammenti di codice all'interno della conversazione, migliorando la comprensione del codice nel contesto.Modalità scura: ChitChat include una modalità scura per una visione più confortevole in condizioni di scarsa illuminazione, riducendo l'affaticamento degli occhi.Funzione di copia degli appunti: Alimentata da ChatGPT, questa estensione consente di copiare facilmente il testo dalla chat agli appunti, particolarmente utile per trasferire informazioni ad altre applicazioni o documenti.Riassunto: con ChitChat, riassumere pagine web o video di YouTube è facile come fare clic con il tasto destro del mouse e selezionare "riassunto". Questa funzione GPT-4 fornisce un riepilogo che permette di risparmiare tempo.Siamo certi che troverete la nostra estensione alimentata da ChatGPT incredibilmente vantaggiosa! Siamo ansiosi di ricevere le vostre recensioni e i vostri commenti. Tutte le traduzioni (come francese, tedesco, spagnolo, arabo e altre novantasette lingue) sono alimentate da traduzioni automatiche neurali di Google Translate che traduce accuratamente i tuoi contenuti.Traduzione con doppio clicSarai in grado di tradurre con un doppio clic per ottenere una rapida traduzione delle parole.Sintesi vocaleUsa la funzione TTS che ti aiuta a imparare come suonano le parole e la trascrizione fonetica.Traduzioni a tutta paginaTraduci intere pagine Web nella lingua desiderata con un solo clic. Questa è una nuova funzionalità fornita gratuitamente da Google Translator che abbiamo integrato nel nostro traduttore.Storia della traduzioneTutta la cronologia delle traduzioni è memorizzata nella memoria locale del tuo browser. Per trovare o eliminare la cronologia delle traduzioni, fai clic sull'icona dell'estensione nell'angolo in alto a destra del browser. Quindi fai clic sull'icona "Mostra cronologia traduzioni" nella finestra pop-up. Questo traduttore non utilizza alcun archivio cloud. Pertanto, dopo aver rimosso l'estensione, tutta la cronologia delle traduzioni verrà eliminata dalla memoria locale del browser senza possibilità di recupero.
name: Traduttore web, dizionario - traduzione semplice

description: Apre il menu utente con strumenti utili (copia, ricerca, traduzione, evidenziazione, ecc.) Quando il testo è selezionato con il… SelectionSK is an extension which automatically pops up the user menu with useful tools (copy, search, translation, highlight, etc.) when the text is selected with the mouse.The idea beyond the extension is that the text is always selected with the purpose, so it is more convenient to automatically popup the menu on selection rather than do it in two steps (select and right mouse click).It's easy, extremely convenient and highly configurable. Give it a try!Let me know if you want other functions added.Note: During initialization the extension will create a 'SelectionSK' bookmark folder under 'Other Bookmarks' and populate it with search and translation urls. Please modify this folder according to your needs.You can you help support extension continued development by making a small contribution: https://www.paypal.me/selectionsk/Functions:   Copy selected text to the clipboard in various ways (standard copy, copy as plain text, copy as html). In addition, the selected text can be copied to clipboard automatically.   Send selected text to pre-configured bookmarks. There are default search\translate\dictionary bookmarks and in addition you can create your own. A lot of pre-configured bookmarks are available on the support site. It is extremely power tool and you can fully adopt it to your own needs - use it for everything from image search to currency convertor.   Right mouse button click opens bookmark with quoted selected text aka 'phrase search'   Middle mouse button click opens bookmark and highlight all occurrences of selected text.   Translate selected text using Google Translate, Wordnik Thesaurus, Urban Dictionary or Yandex Dictionary. Translation can be copied to the clipboard. Text-to-speech is available for both, original text and translation. In addition, translation window has a link onto page where full definition of translated text (for instance, pronunciation or usage examples) can be obtained.   Open the text as a URL. Text will be validating for the URL in a smart way – in addition to well-formed URLs, the extension will check broken URLs (for instance, without http prefix) and href attribute. Obfuscated URLs and email addresses like "hxxp://website(dot)name(dot)com" or "mail(at)provider(dot)com" will be detected and de-obfuscated.   Open or copy to clipboard multiple URLs at the same time instead of having to do them all individually.   Highlight all occurrences of the selected text. More than one word or phrase can be highlighted with different color. Move forward\backward in between highlighted phrases using 'W' and 'S'. Remove highlighting by pressing 'Esc'.   Select currency with its symbol or abbreviation and convert it into desired currency.   Panel mode: a small panel with icons only will appear instead of a popup menu.   Unobtrusive mode: small, unobtrusive button will appear instead of popup menu. Popup menu will be activated if user clicks on the button or if user holds mouse cursor on the button for a second.   Context menu: send selected text to pre-configured bookmarks using traditional context menu.   Send the selection to the mail recipient. A new email window will be opened using mailto: protocol, selected text will be added as email body. In addition, selection will be copied to the clipboard, which allows to insert it to the email from the clipboard (useful if selection has images or rich html).   Toolbar icon provides a shortcuts to enable\disable extension on certain site (left mouse click) or to preferences and page translation (right mouse click). Whole page can be also translated by pressing Ctrl+Shift+0.   Translate on demand, type 't <your word or phrase>' in the address bar.The extension is also available for Firefox at https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/selectionsk/.SelectionSK will send selected text to online translators in order to get it translated. Please read their privacy policies.Thank you for being interested in SelectionSK. Please submit your suggestions and report issues on https://bitbucket.org/ashemetov/selectionsk/issues.You can contribute by helping translate SelectionSK on Crowdin: https://crwd.in/selectionsk.
name: SelectionSK

Individuare le idee commerciali di tendenza prima che diventino mainstream.➤ Affidato a oltre 10.000 utenti..."Utilizziamo l'estensione g-trends di Glimpse per comprendere i cambiamenti di interesse dei consumatori nel tempo e, in effetti, si tratta di una vera e propria svolta".  - Emily Wilson, direttore della gestione dei prodotti, Netflix"Ottimo strumento per tutti i marketer del settore SEO o PPC. Rispetto allo strumento predefinito, aggiunge molta più profondità se si cerca di identificare nuove parole chiave di tendenza e/o correlate". - Alex Lowe, Direttore SEO, NKP Medical➤ FAQDomanda: Che cos'è Google Trends?Risposta: Google Trends è uno strumento realizzato da  Google che consente al pubblico di vedere l'attività di ricerca aggregata nel tempo per qualsiasi parola chiave, compreso il filtro per regione, paese e città.Domanda: Come leggere google trends?Risposta: Mentre in genere è necessario confrontare le parole chiave per capire il volume relativo, Glimpse Chrome Extension consente di vedere il volume di ricerca assoluto delle parole chiave in Google Trends.Domanda: Google trends è accurato?Risposta: Google Trends è probabilmente lo strumento più accurato per il volume delle parole chiave. La coerenza dei modelli nella stagionalità giornaliera, settimanale e mensile dimostra la qualità dei dati e la loro accuratezza.Domanda: In che modo un inserzionista può trarre vantaggio dall'utilizzo di google trends?Risposta: Google Trends consente agli inserzionisti di vedere la frequenza con cui determinati termini vengono ricercati su Internet. Queste informazioni aiutano gli inserzionisti a ottimizzare le loro campagne e a concentrarsi sulle parole chiave comunemente utilizzate dai potenziali clienti. Inoltre, Google Trends può aiutare gli inserzionisti a identificare le tendenze nel comportamento dei clienti e ad adattare le loro strategie di conseguenza.Domanda: Come interpretare Google Trends?Risposta: Può essere difficile interpretare l'"interesse nel tempo" nell'applicazione standard. Molte persone confrontano due termini per avere un'idea del volume relativo. Fortunatamente, il componente aggiuntivo <Glimpse> aggiunge il volume assoluto.Domanda: Cosa significa "interesse di google trends nel tempo"?Risposta: "Interesse nel tempo" in Google Trends si riferisce alle ricerche nel tempo. Inoltre, è possibile filtrare per geografia, dal livello di paese a quello di città.Domanda: Come si procura Glimpse i dati di ricerca?Risposta: La nostra estensione raccoglie metriche da un'ampia varietà di fonti, tra cui google trends india, google trends uk, google trends us, google trends canada e tutte le altre aree geografiche. Oltre alla ricerca, analizziamo anche i dati dei consumatori su altre 12 piattaforme principali.Domanda: Esiste un'app Google Trends?Risposta: Purtroppo no. La cosa più simile è l'esperienza predefinita di Google Trends con l'estensione Glimpse per Chrome installata.
name: Glimpse – Google Trends Supercharged

For all uses of this name, use this The My Hero Academia Boku No to show love ♥.My Hero Academia (僕のヒーローアカデミア Boku no Hīrō Akademia?) is a Japanese superhero manga series written and illustrated by Kōhei Horikoshi. It has been serialized in Weekly Shōnen Jump since July 2014 and 12 volumes have been collected in tankōbon format. The series has been licensed for English-language release by Viz Media, and began serialization in their weekly digital manga anthology Weekly Shonen Jump on February 9, 2015. The story follows Izuku Midoriya, a boy born without superpowers in a world where they are the norm, but who still dreams of becoming a superhero himself, and is scouted by the world's greatest hero who shares his powers with Izuku after recognizing his value and enrolls him in a high school for heroes in training. The manga was adapted into an anime television series; the first season aired from April 3 to June 26, 2016,and a second season premiered on April 1, 2017.

description: Top Event Rental Tips for Your Amazing EventAre you planning out an event? Planning an event could be a daunting task when you do… Top Event Rental Tips for Your Amazing EventAre you planning out an event? Planning an event could be a daunting task when you do not have access to the desirable resources. Right from the conceptualization of the idea to its final implementation, you need to ensure that every aspect of your event is perfect for the guests. In case you are skeptical about organizing an amazing event all on yourself, you can consider taking professional help from some event rentals company. By doing so, you can be assured of the best-in-class event management services offered as per your specific event needs.When you have basic event knowledge and collective efforts of the event rentals staff & teams, a successful event can turn out to be a rewarding endeavor. Different types of events might require different event rentals. Here are some major event rental tips that could transform your dull event into a rocking one seamlessly:•	Table Rentals: The selection of the table rentals might range from community Harvest tables to cocktail tables, seated events, formal dinner tables, large rounded top tables, rectangular tables, and so more. For events like corporate meetings, you might require to set up the area with cocktail tables for encouraging effective communication amongst the event guests. Similarly, the less formal events like a casual party could go forward with setting up communal tables & benches for the event guests. The choice of the tables would majorly vary depending on the chosen event venue & theme. As such, you can consider creating a proper floor plan that tends to best utilize the available space at the event venue.•	Chair Rentals: It can be sometimes highly intuitive to choose the best table & chair arrangement at the given event venue. For instance, harvest communal tables usually go well with matching benches or chairs. Similarly, the cocktail tables might call up for bar stools. For ceremonies or events requiring longer duration, you can go forward with installing folding chairs as the economical option out there. However, you must also pay attention to setting up chairs with proper padding towards ensuring the overall comfort of the guests. For high-end events like wedding, corporate events, or receptions, elegantly-styled Chiavari chairs are a popular option. •	Linen: When it comes to high-end, upscale events like weddings, receptions, or corporate events, the choice of the perfect linen could play a major role in uplifting the overall décor of the event. Linen must be selected on the basis of the event theme. Right from choosing the linen color palette to the pattern, texture, and other factors –select the best linen depending on the theme of the given event. You should not just think about the color of the linen. The factors like material and texture also matter a lot. An outdoor barbeque event could go for installing linen options like some basic poly-cotton fabric. On the other hand, a simple holiday party can be best suited with elegant napkins & tabletops. •	Furniture: Most of the high-class event planners go forward with choosing the perfect furniture items including couches, coffee tables, and armchairs at both outdoor as well as indoor events. It is advisable to go for choosing furniture that tends to complement the overall theme & color of the particular event. You can try out mixing & matching different textures & color palettes for creating a beautiful visual appeal. The furniture pieces at events could also include stages, dance floors, and other elements that are meant for the purpose of entertainment. You must choose the furniture on the basis of event type & theme. •	Décor: The overall décor of the event tends to be the most personalized element of any event. Piping & draping, lighting fixtures, centerpieces, wall décor, and other essential décor items must all reflect the theme of the event. Make sure you take care of these event rental tips for an everlasting event!
name: Party rental catalog

description: What is this app about?In this app you will get a great collections of ebooks which are on public domain and about pirates.How… What is this app about?In this app you will get a great collections of ebooks which are on public domain and about pirates.How is an ebook worksNow that in the market there are already many models to choose from, the consumer will be clear on what to call electronic book and what not. We will also leave aside mobile phones and other devices, including ultraportable, TabletPC or directly computers, which allow us to read electronic book formats but that do not interest us for this special. Let's forget them then.For us the electronic book is a compact device, in the form of a traditional book (rectangular as a rule) and whose most important element is the screen . Currently, the screen sizes of e-books are between 6 and 10 inches, with a clear predominance of books with 6-inch screens.These screens are not capable of displaying more than black and white content, with different levels of gray scales depending on the model we choose. These levels of grays usually fluctuate between 4 and 16. In the future, there is already some model of little success, those screens will be in color.The models of current electronic books are relatively light (from just over 150 grams to almost half a kilo of some model with little future) and of contained thickness, of average 1 cm.The resolution of the screen also varies according to the size of the same, but the most common models offer two mainly: 1024 × 768 pixels for larger models and 800 × 600 pixels for the most common 6 inches.How we put content to the e-book readerThe most common ports in an e-book reader are two: USB and slot for memory cards. The first one is also responsible for recharging the internal battery of the equipment.They are also the most common to introduce the methods contained in the book. If the internal memory of the book address is wide, we can leave there our collection of digital books. For them we will normally use the USB connection from the book to the computer. It will behave as a unit more mass storage and only have to drag and drop . This way is how we access content purchased from an online store, which we generally downloaded to your computer first and then pass on to our portable reader.If the internal memory of our electronic book is not too broad and is almost testimonial, the memory card becomes the main storage system. Of course, we will have to have it always placed in the electronic book.Connectivity, what gives life to the bookA third method to have electronic books in our reader is to use the wireless connectivity of the same. If it is, because there are still few models that incorporate it. And they are usually the most expensive.The electronic books are opting for two types of connection with the outside: WiFi and 3G . The most interesting of both is 3G connectivity, because with WiFi we continue to depend on a network close to which we have access. In addition, the content that we can download does not usually have much size.The most commercial books already come with 3G connectivity . In this case, we do not depend on a WiFi network. With the help of these 3G networks, readers often give us access to the online store of the company that markets the specific model as well as to subscriptions to magazines, newspapers and even Internet publications. The Sony Reader or the Amazon Kindle are very clear examples.
name: Unlimited Books

description: Nordicmakten (NM) er et tekstbasert mafiaspill. Målet er å bygge opp sin mafiabruker ved å utføre kriminelle handlinger, kjøpe og… Nordicmakten (NM) er et tekstbasert mafiaspill. Målet er å bygge opp sin mafiabruker ved å utføre kriminelle handlinger, kjøpe og selge varer, utføre oppdrag, delta i forumdiskusjoner, samt spille taktisk og klokt. Jo mer aktiv du er, jo fortere vil du gå opp i rank. Spiller du riktig, er du kanskje en av de få som når den prestisjefylte ranken Capo Don. Opparbeider du deg en god økonomi, er muligheten til stedet for at du kan skaffe deg ditt eget firma! Det finnes også gjenger på spillet. Hver gjeng har sitt eget forum, og en egen oversikt over sine meritter og sin statistikk. Er du et potensielt gjengmedlem, eller kanskje en beintøff gjengleder? Eller liker du muligens å spille solo uten gjengtilhørighet? - Valget er ditt.SPILLHISTORIENordicmakten er oppfølgeren til det berømte spillet Nordicmafia.net, som i 2005-2011 var ledende innenfor denne spillsjangeren med flere tusen aktive spillere. På slutten dalte aktiviteten til den daværende NM-ledelsen, og høsten 2011 ble spillet lagt ned - til gjenværende spilleres forferdelse. Året etter ble spillet kodet helt på nytt av nye eiere med diverse forbedringer, og 28. september 2012 ble spillet offisielt åpnet for spillerne. Siden den tid har spillermassen økt sakte, men sikkert, og både gamle og nye NM-skikkelser har returnert for å ta del i den virtuelle mafiaverdenen. Nordicmakten har kommet for å gjenerobre mafiatittelen. Ta del i NM-samfunnet, du også!
name: Nordicmakten.com

description: Itinatag noong February 2005, ang YouTube ang pinakasikat na online na komunidad ng video sa mundo, na nagbibigay-daan sa… Itinatag noong February 2005, ang YouTube ang pinakasikat na online na komunidad ng video sa mundo, na nagbibigay-daan sa milyun-milyong tao na makatuklas, makapanood at makapamahagi ng orihinal na ginawang mga video. Nagibibigay ang YouTube ng forum upang makipag-ugnay, magpabatid, at magpukaw sa ibang mga tao sa buong mundo at kumikilos bilang platform ng pagbabahagi para sa mga tagalikha ng orihinal na nilalaman at malalaki at maliliit na advertiser.   Binibigyang-daan ng YouTube ang mga tao na makapag-download at makapagbahagi ng mga video clip nang madali sa www.YouTube.com at sa buong Internet sa pamamagitan ng mga website, mga mobile device, mga blog, at e-mail.Sinuman ay maaaring makilahok sa komunidad ng YouTube sa pamamagitan ng panonoood, pagbabahagi, at pagbibigay ng komento sa mga video. Makakakita ang tao ng first-hand na mga account ng kasalukuyang mga kaganapan, buhayin muli ang kanilang mga paboritong sandali sa TV, maghanap ng mga video tungkol sa kanilang mga hilig at interes, makatuklas ng mga bagong artista at mga tagalikha ng pelikula, at maging ang maglantad ng kakaiba at pambihira.Habang mas maraming tao ang kumukuha ng mga espesyal na sandali sa video, binibigyang-daan sila ng YouTube na makapagbahagi ng kanilang mga karanasan, mga talento, at kahusayan sa mundo.  Ang ilan sa mga tampok ng site ay kinabibilangan ng:*Pag-embed ng video: Makakapagpasok ng isang video sa YouTube ang mga user sa mga account ng Facebook at MySpace, mga blog, o iba pang mga Web site kung saan kahit sino ay makakapanood.*Mga pampubliko o pribadong video: Makakaboto ang mga user na isahimpapawid ang kanilang mga video sa publiko o ibahagi ang mga ito nang pribado sa mga kaibigan at pamilya pagka-upload.*Mga subscription: Nasusubaybayan ng mga user ang mga bagong video ng kanilang mga paboritong user.*Mag-record mula sa Webcam: May kakayahan ang mga user na may mga webcam at Flash na software na mag-record ng mga tugon sa video o mga normal na video sa isang site sa halip na mag-record muna bago ma-upload ang video.*TestTube: Ito ay isang area kung saan ang mga engineer at mga nag-develop ng YouTube ay nagsasagawa ng alpha na pagsubok para sa mga bagong tampok na nililinang. Hinihikayat ang mga user na makilahok sa mga proseso ng paglinang at malugod na tinatanggap ang pagsuri sa tampok. Sa pamamagitan ng pagrehistro, ang mga user ay nakakapag-upload at nakakpagbahagi ng mga video, nakakapag-save ng mga paborito, nakakalikha ng mga playlist at komento sa mga video. Bumubuo ang YouTube ng isang komunidad na lubos na ganadong manood at magbahagi ng mga video. Ang serbisyo ng YouTube ay libre at susuportahan ng advertising.  Isang bahagi ng layunin ng YouTube ay mapalawig ang pag-abot nito sa mga Internet browser at bigyang-daan ang mga user na makatuklas at makapagbahagi ng mga nakakahimok na nilalaman ng video. Bilang bahagi nito, ipinagpapatuloy ng YouTube ang pagsisimula at pagpapahusay sa mga API at mga tool nito. Kinabibilangan ito ng wholesale na access sa malawak na video library, madla sa buong mundo, at saligang video hosting at streaming na imprastraktura  na nagpapagana sa site, na nagbibigay sa mga user ng isa pa muling paraan upang makisangkot sa mundo ng video at aktibong makilahok sa komunidad ng YouTube nasaan man sila, kailanman nila naisin.
name: YouTube

description: THIS IS THE CANARY DISTRIBUTION OF THE METAMASK EXTENSION, INTENDED FOR DEVELOPERS. MetaMask Flask is a distribution channel of the MetaMask extension for developers that gives them access to additional unstable APIs. The goal of Flask is to maximize developer control, so that we can learn the full extent of what developers want to do with MetaMask, and later incorporate those lessons into the main MetaMask distribution.You can find the main / production version of MetaMask here: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/metamask/nkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknnMetaMask is an extension for accessing Ethereum enabled distributed applications, or "Dapps" in your browser!The extension injects the Ethereum web3 API into every website's javascript context, so that dapps can read from the blockchain.MetaMask also lets the user create and manage their own identities (via private keys, local client wallet and hardware wallets like Trezor™), so when a Dapp wants to perform a transaction and write to the blockchain, the user gets a secure interface to review the transaction, before approving or rejecting it.Because it adds functionality to the normal browser context, MetaMask requires the permission to read and write to any webpage. You can always "view the source" of MetaMask the way you do any Chrome extension, or view the source code on Github:https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-extensionEnables access to:Web 3.0DappsNFTserc20tokensICOserc271...and more!
name: MetaMask Flask DEVELOPMENT BUILD

description: What is a Software Development Process?Development of software product is difficult during the earlier days. A proper mechanism… What is a Software Development Process?Development of software product is difficult during the earlier days. A proper mechanism is followed via successive phases which reduce the cost and time of the software products.  There are varieties of tasks and activities with the proper approach are followed during every single process. So, software development process is the mechanized life cycle of any development of software in a structured manner. For every single process complete set of instructions followed.The software development company implements proper well-verified process methodologies during any software product development. Do you know every organization always follow one of the leading models during software development known as CMM Capability Maturity Model? The organizations and companies provided with grading systems such as ISO 9000, Six Sigma, and much more according to how well they create and undergo with the execution of processes of the software products. During school and college days we studied the software development lifecycles steps, but at that time we only mug and write during exams about what is software development life cycle. As compared to student life while working in companies only difference is to analyze the proper mechanism and implement proper strategies to reach the output during software product development. Here are the proper activities and steps of software engineering process –1.	What is the requirement?What is the software product about? What are the main requirements for its development? How do customers respond to it? How easily the software products solve the customer’s problems? We have to think and analyze during the first phase of software product development.2.	What are the proper specifications?How to write the software product so it precisely describes every single task? How software Development Company describes the rigorous mathematics involve during the software product development? Specifications for Safety and security with easy to use the application are well written by the programmers.3.	Architecture of the SoftwareUnder this software development, life cycle phase professionals define the abstract representation of the system. It means that the software met with the original requirements of the product. In this phase one of the most important requirements can be addressed and that is–ensuring the future requirements of the software product.4.	ImplementationThe designed system is now reduced to coding format. 5.	TestingWhen any software product launch to the market, then it is a beta software product which is tested by the consumers, but prior to that continuous testing undergoes during this phase by several testers and software engineers on the vivid functionality of the product.6.	Proper DocumentationWhat about the future maintenance and enhancement of the software product? It is a Good idea and important task to do proper documentation of the internal design of the worked product.7.	Provide Support Training After development, the most beautiful work comes which is responsible for any product huge demand around the market. Success and failure of product - It all depends on the Training and support provided to users who are using the software product.8.	MaintenanceIt is the top requirement after the launch to maintain the software adding new features, developing new features so the software is not outdated from the market. It believed that 40% of engineering work maintenance, but it is not true the maintenance is all about nearly 10 to 20% after the product development by software Development Company.
name: Vironit

description: Kumuha ng mga buod para sa anumang balita, website, o video sa YouTube sa isang iglap gamit ang ChatGPT. Makatipid ng oras ✓… Introducing the ChatGPT Suite - the ultimate tool for easy and efficient web page summarization! With just a few clicks, you can now summarize any web page or Youtube video.💡 Saves time & gets the key points without the fluff! Learn more in less time!🌟 Features• Summarizes any website with GPT.• Summarizes the transcript of any Youtube Video.• Uses templates to modify the result for study, science or journalistic purposes. • Support of the official OpenAI API• Markdown rendering• Dark mode📜 Changelog:1.0.6.• support for the fast and cheap gpt-3.5-turbo API Key.1.0.5• Bugfix: some Youtube videos did not work.1.0.4• Design: Improved new Layout1.0.3• Bugfix: some requests did not work reliable (too long)• Design: Improved error handling.1.0.2• Feature: full Youtube Transcription Support• Feature: Caching for results• Feature: more languages🔮 Features to come:• ask me anything feature about the text! (AMA)• split content in chunks to work with the character limit of ChatGPT.• more default question templates (for private purpose, news, podcasts, student and educational content, science, journalists, reviews, tutorials ...)• chat history and continuing conversations across tabs• jump marks in videos und text (sophisticated :)) but possible• Prompts for the Bing API and for Google Bard or LLaMA (everywhere :))💡 Template Ideas / PromptsBe creative with the question in ChatGPT to summarize any content, post it into the ratings or drop us a note to share it.-- Study & Research Template (Example I)Please summarize the paper by author(s) in one concise sentence. Then, list key insights with an emoji in front of it and lessons learned from the paper. Next, generate 3-5 questions that you would like to ask the authors about their work. Finally, provide 3-5 suggestions for related topics or future research directions based on the content of the paper. If applicable, list at least 5 relevant references from the field of study of the paper. The url to extract facts from is this: {{URL}}. If the url has a paywall or no content use this text:  {{CONTENT}}---- Easy SummarySummarize the following text with the most unique and helpful points, into a numbered list of key points and takeaways: {{CONTENT}}---- Youtube Chapter Summary You must only reply with one chapter and you must also reply in {{SELECTED_LANGUAGE}}, here is the required format for your reply: 'Chapter {{TITLE}}: [appropriate number of bullet points]', your chapter must be enjoyable to read and must not leave the reader in the dark for a moment, you must expand on your points if necessary for the reader to understand and you can add your own knowledge if needed, you must be very specific in your chapter, do not be vague in the slightest because this must be an adequate substitute for actually watching the video, here is only a part of the transcript text you must summarise: {{CONTENT}}---- Research Analyst StyleYou are a research analyst. I will provide you with a section of a document and you will create a summary from it. You will use your editing and writing skills to create a summary in the style of a Confidential Information Memorandum. You will preserve as many details as possible. You will maintain context across the summary. Your section will be combined with the other sections to create summary of the entire document.Your summary must be no longer than 650 characters long.---- Copy EditorYou are a copyeditor. Combine the below summaries. The combined output must be less than 4,000 characters long. You must keep the content and context preserved. ---- Advanced TLDR (too long to read) for the davinci modelWe introduce Extreme TLDR generation, a new form of extreme summarization for paragraphs. TLDR generation involves high source compression, removes stop words and summarizes the paragraph whilst retaining meaning. The result is the shortest possible summary that retains all of the original meaning and context of the paragraph.ExampleParagraph:{{CONTENT}}Extreme TLDR--🚫 Limits:• Fact Check! » Neural Networks and AI language models like ChatGPT might hallucinate facts (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hallucination_(artificial_intelligence))• ChatGPT can only reply one question at a time and needs some time especially in the free version.• has a character limit for its input at the moment and ChatGPT might sometimes not summarize the whole text (Limit: ~16000 character in GPT Youtube Summaries)• Use ChatGPT Plus to get more speed and less over capacity errors for your Summary.🧑🏻‍💻 Open Source Extension:- https://github.com/(in progress, would love to share & help)- OpenAI & ChatGPT Source: https://github.com/openai/(Note: this ChatGPT extension is not related to or associated with ChatGPT or OpenAI.)📢 Disclaimer• Short: The extension itself is open source and does not collect any information.• Be aware that any content you summarize with the help of ChatGPT is subject of the OpenAI privacy statement : https://openai.com/privacy/• The ChatGPT Suite extension is not related to or associated with ChatGPT or OpenAI.
name: ChatGPT - Mga Buod ng Website at Video sa YouTube

description: Portal do Feirão do Imposto 2016.O Feirão do Imposto nasceu em 2002, em Joinville, Santa Catarina. Seu propósito de disseminar… Portal do Feirão do Imposto 2016.O Feirão do Imposto nasceu em 2002, em Joinville, Santa Catarina. Seu propósito de disseminar informação tributária de forma simplificada à população tornou a ação conhecida nacionalmente. Atualmente capitaneada pela Confederação Nacional do Jovem Empresário, o Feirão do Imposto acontece em 24 estados da federação e mais de 100 cidades do Brasil. Neste ano de 2016, além de abordar a quantidade de tributos incidentes sobre produtos e serviços, o Feirão do Imposto tratará sobre aplicação dos recursos públicos, ou seja, como tem ocorrido o retorno destes tributos em prol da população. O tema da Campanha 2016 antecipa a reflexão: Bumerangue do Imposto, o único que vai e não volta! Dia 21 de maio, participe do Feirão do Imposto na sua cidade!

description: Password Alert aiuta a proteggere dagli attacchi di phishing. Se inserisci la tua password di Gmail o Google for Work in un sito diverso da accounts.google.com, riceverai un avviso, in modo da poter modificare la password, se necessario.Password Alert cerca anche di individuare le pagine di accesso di Google false e ti avvisa prima che tu abbia digitato la password. A tal fine, Password Alert controlla il codice HTML di ogni pagina che visiti per verificare se si tratta di una pagina di accesso di Google falsa.Domande frequenti (FAQ)-- Quando viene attivata l'estensione Password Alert?Password Alert si attiverà la prossima volta che inserirai la tua password su accounts.google.com.-- Password Alert memorizza la password o le sequenze di tasti?No. Password Alert non memorizza la password o le sequenze di tasti. Memorizza, invece, una miniatura sicura della password, che viene confrontata con una miniatura delle tue sequenze di tasti più recenti all'interno di Chrome.-- Dove invia i dati Password Alert?Se la utilizzi in un account Gmail, Password Alert non invia alcun dato dal computer locale. Se il tuo amministratore di Google for Work sceglie di implementare Password Alert nel tuo dominio, riceverà avvisi quando viene attivata Password Alert.-- Quali sono i limiti di Password Alert?Password Alert non protegge le finestre di navigazione in incognito, le app di Chrome o le estensioni di Chrome. Inoltre, non protegge le password per i servizi non Google. Password Alert funziona solo all'interno del browser web Chrome quando è abilitato JavaScript.-- Dove posso trovare maggiori informazioni?Consulta l'elenco completo di domande frequenti (FAQ) presente all'indirizzo https://support.google.com/a/answer/6197508. In alternativa, puoi visualizzare l'intero codebase open-source all'indirizzo https://github.com/google/password-alert.Installando questa estensione, accetti i Termini di servizio e le Norme sulla privacy di Google all'indirizzo www.google.com/policies/
name: Password Alert

description: Conversations is an open source Jabber / XMPP client for Android compatible smart phones.Design principles• Be as beautiful and… Conversations is an open source Jabber / XMPP client for Android compatible smart phones.Design principles• Be as beautiful and easy to use as possible without sacrificing security or privacy• Rely on existing, well established protocols• Require as little permissions as possibleFeatures• End-to-end encryption with either OMEMO, OTR or OpenPGP• Sending and receiving images• Pictures / Avatars for your Contacts• Syncs with desktop client• Conferences (with support for bookmarks)• Address book integration• Multiple Accounts / unified inbox• Very low impact on battery lifeXMPP FeaturesConversations works with every XMPP server out there. However XMPP is an extensible protocol. These extensions are standardized as well in so called XEP’s. Conversations supports a couple of those to make the overall user experience better. There is a chance that your current XMPP server does not support these extensions. Therefore to get the most out of Conversations you should consider either switching to anXMPP server that does or - even better - run your own XMPP server for you and your friends.These XEPs are - as of now:• XEP-0065: SOCKS5 Bytestreams (or mod_proxy65). Will be used to transfer files if both parties are behind a firewall (NAT).• XEP-0163: Personal Eventing Protocol for avatars• XEP-0191: Blocking command lets you blacklist spammers or block contacts without removing them from your roster.• XEP-0198: Stream Management allows XMPP to survive small network outages and changes of the underlying TCP connection.• XEP-0280: Message Carbons which automatically syncs the messages you send to your desktop client and thus allows you to switch seamlessly from your mobile client to your desktop client and back within one conversation.• XEP-0237: Roster Versioning mainly to save bandwidth on poor mobile connections• XEP-0313: Message Archive Management synchronize message history with the server. Catch up with messages that were sent while Conversations was offline.• XEP-0352: Client State Indication lets the server know whether or not Conversations is in the background. Allows the server to save bandwidth by withholding unimportant packages.• XEP-0363: HTTP File Upload allows you to share files in conferences and with offline contacts. Requires an additional component on your server.
name: Conversations

description: Rimuove gli elementi di tracciamento dagli URL. This extension will automatically remove tracking elements from URLs to help protect your privacy when browse through the Internet.Many websites use tracking elements in the URL (e.g. https://example.com?utm_source=newsletter1&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=sale)  to mark your online activity. All that tracking code is not necessary for a website to be displayed or work correctly and can therefore be removed—that is exactly what ClearURLs does. Another common example are Amazon URLs. If you search for a product on Amazon you will see a very long URL, such as: https://www.amazon.com/dp/exampleProduct/ref=sxin_0_pb?__mk_de_DE=ÅMÅŽÕÑ&keywords=tea&pd_rd_i=exampleProduct&pd_rd_r=8d39e4cd-1e4f-43db-b6e7-72e969a84aa5&pd_rd_w=1pcKM&pd_rd_wg=hYrNl&pf_rd_p=50bbfd25-5ef7-41a2-68d6-74d854b30e30&pf_rd_r=0GMWD0YYKA7XFGX55ADP&qid=1517757263&rnid=2914120011Indeed most of the above URL is tracking code. Once ClearURLs has cleaned the address, it will look like this:https://www.amazon.com/dp/exampleProductAll functions in a nutshell* Removes tracking from URLs automatically in the background* Blocks some common ad domains (optional)* Has a built-in tool to clean up multiple URLs at once* Supports redirection to the destination, without tracking services as middleman* Adds an entry to the context menu so that links can be copied quickly and cleanly* Blocks hyperlink auditing, also known as ping tracking* Prevents tracking injection over history API* Prevents Google from rewriting the search results (to include tracking elements)* Prevents Yandex from rewriting the search results (to include tracking elements)* Badgeds to show the currently blocked elements* Supports optional logging* Supports export/import of settings* Has a donate button
name: ClearURLs

description: Amazon Discount Finder ti aiuta a trovare le migliori offerte di prodotti Amazon fino a 90% di sconto. L'acquisto su Amazon è una piacevole esperienza sicuramente data la varietà dei prodotti disponibili ed è davvero il miglior sito di shopping online, utilizzato da tanti utenti per i loro acquisti via Internet. Uno dei problemi di Amazon e, allo stesso tempo, il suo punto di forza: è davvero enorme!Amazon offre tonnellate di offerte e sconti ogni giorno, ma districarsi attraverso le infinite pagine del sito non è facile e può capitare di perdere una buonissima occasione solo perché ci è sfuggita.Spesso offre i migliori sconti di tutto il web, che possono arrivare anche fino al 75% su alcuni prodotti, ma il sito (giustamente) indirizza le persone in altre aree con prodotti con margini più alti di profitto, facendo passare le grandi offerte in sezioni specifiche o addirittura “in sordina”.Il modo per approfittare di questi sconti è un po' complicato, poiché consiste nel manipolare l'url per includere alcuni parametri che indicano di cercare sconti. L'obiettivo di questo strumento è di renderlo accessibile a tutti, in modo che anche voi possiate approfittare con facilità di queste occasioni.----------------* COME SI USA: *----------------1. Selezionare il negozio Amazon (paese) nel quale si desidera cercare il prodotto;2. Selezionare una Categoria, se si desidera cercare prodotti scontati all’interno di una categoria selezionata;3. Oppure inserire una parola chiave (keyword) e cercare le migliori offerte, cliccando il tasto "Cerca”.4. La keyword (parola chiave) in realtà non è necessaria se si desidera esplorare solo i prodotti disponibili nella categoria selezionata.--------------------* CARATTERISTICHE: *--------------------1. Fornisce opzioni avanzate di ricerca su Amazon.2. Disponibile per tutti i paesi: Stati Uniti, Canada, Regno Unito, Germania, Francia, Italia, Spagna, Giappone e Cina.3. Ricerca in base ad una keyword inserita.4. Ricerca a seconda del range di sconto impostato: è possibile cercare tutti i prodotti con sconti dal 1% al 99%.5. Risultati della ricerca opzionali ordinati per:• Bestseller• Rilevanza• Prezzo: crescente• Prezzo: decrescente• In ordine alfabetico• Media recensioni clienti6. Ricerca per fascia di prezzo: l'utente può immettere un range di prezzi per i quali si desidera vedere i risultati.--------------------* SUGGERIMENTI: *--------------------Per un'esperienza più completa e soddisfacente possibile, non dimenticate i seguenti suggerimenti:• Non rimanere nella prima paginaCercare occasioni è come una caccia al tesoro, non si arriva e si trova una X rossa sotto la palma, ma bisogna anche scavare per trovare il tesoro. Una volta cliccato sul pulsante "Cerca" potrebbe essere necessario scorrere la pagina, oppure andare alla pagina successiva nella ricerca o tornare alla home per perfezionarlo. La pazienza è la madre della scienza!• È corretto lo sconto?I link che forniamo sono generati in modo completamente automatico, quindi è possibile che alcuni url non siano corretti.• Uno sconto non è sempre un affareChe un prodotto abbia uno sconto non significa che non sia possibile trovarlo più conveniente altrove.• Spedizione GratuitaA volte qualcosa di semplice come l'acquisto di un prodotto che costa poco può far risparmiare spese di spedizione. Amazon ha tariffe di spedizione abbastanza ragionevoli, ma che un risparmiatore consapevole vorrebbe sempre evitare.Da notare che le tariffe di spedizione Amazon dipendono fortemente dalla sezione in cui si acquista, dai soldi spesi o se avete Amazon Prime. Il nostro consiglio è che se l'acquisto non raggiunge il minimo, trascorrete un po' di tempo in più su qualche piccola cosa per completare la spesa minima di 19 EUR. Cercare di acquistare qualcosa che si stava andando a comprare comunque, perché se no, il risparmio sarà solo psicologico.--------------------ENGLISH--------------------Amazon is really the best online shopping site, and often it offers 75% and better reductions, yet it directs people to other areas, sending them to higher profit margin products instead.There's a geeky way to manipulate Amazon's web links to display all heavily-reduced bargains. All you need to do is fiddle with Amazon web addresses to bring up lists of knock-down prices.The problem is these are a faff to make yourself. So we built the Amazon Hidden Discount Finder. It creates your own bespoke super-specific pages in seconds, where you choose the discount.Our Discount Finder manipulates Amazon web-links to create customized bargain basement pages. Just select the percent off the list price & the category you want, eg, TVs 30%+ off or DVDs 90%+ off.We would love to hear any feedback on the answers it gives, any new categories you'd like added and other suggestions. It would also be fab if you could add any top Amazon discount links you find and other Amazon buying tips that we haven't included in the guide below the tool.--------------* HOW TO USE *--------------1. Select the Amazon store (country) in which you want to search for the product;2. Select a category, if you want to search for discounted products within a selected category;3. Or enter a keyword (keyword) and find the best deals, by clicking the "Search" button.4. The keyword is not really necessary if you want to explore only the products available in the selected category.---------* Tips: *---------• When searching for treasure, don't just look at the first page of bargains, try a few. Don't assume that just because it's discounted, it must be a good buy. Try higher percentage discounts for cheaper, smaller items and lower percentages for niche, expensive ones.Just because something is listed with a huge discount, it doesn't automatically make it a bargain (or worth buying).-------------* Features: *-------------1. Provides advanced search options on Amazon.2. Available for all countries: US, Canada, UK, Germany, France, Italy, Spain, Japan and China.3. Research on the basis of a keyword inserted.4. Search according to the range set off: you can search all products with discounts from 1% to 99%.5. Search results optional sorted by:• Bestsellers• New and Popular• Price: Low to High• Price: High to Low• Average Customer Review6. By price range: the user can set a range of prices for which you want to see results.--------------------FRANÇAIS--------------------Le site marchand d'Amazon.fr est tellement vaste qu'il n'est pas très facile de s'y retrouver surtout pour trouver les articles en promotion en cours, c'est là qu'intervient le Cerca Sconti pour trouver plus aisément les rabais sur Amazon.fr.Facile a utiliser, Cerca Sconti agit comme un moteur de recherche auquel il faut spécifier en premier lieu la langue, le drapeau français pour Amazon.fr puis sélectionnez une rubrique et le nom de l'article désiré et ensuite le taux minimum de réduction (ne rêvez pas trop quand même) avant de cliquer sur le bouton Rechercher.En option, il y a la possibilité de filtrer le prix et trier les résultats par pertinence, par prix croissants, note moyenne des commentaires, comme sur Amazon.Cerca Sconti, Trouvez des rabais cachés sur Amazon. Remise Finder vous permet de trouver les meilleures offres jusqu'à 90% de réduction.--------------------ESPAÑOL--------------------Descubre nuestro buscador de ofertas en amazon.es y no te pierdas ni una ganga más. Selecciona la categoría, el porcentaje de descuento, límite de precio, busca por texto y mucho más.El comprar en Amazon.es es una experiencia sin duda placentera dada la variedad de productos de los que disponen. Además, gracias a nuestro buscador de ofertas es también placentero (o no tan doloroso) para nuestro bolsillo. Los mejores trucos para ahorrar en tus compras con Amazon.esEn esta lista de trucos para el gigante Amazon encontrarás los mejores consejos para disfrutar de los precios más atractivos. Además, incluye el buscador de descuentos para Amazon que inmediatamente te redirige a la sección de tu interés con los criterios de búsqueda que definas y te permite filtrar por el porcentaje de descuento deseado. Así conseguirás las mejores gangas en electrónica, televisores, ordenadores, kindle, libros, etc. En definitiva, podrás comprar tus productos en Amazon a un precio todavía mejor.Cosas importantes a comprobar:Para que nuestra experiencia sea lo más completa y satisfactoria posible, no está de más no olvidar los siguientes consejos:• No te quedes en la primera páginaBuscar gangas es como buscar un tesoro, no llegas y te encuentras una X roja bajo una palmera, excavas y encuentras el oro de Cortés. Una vez hayas hecho click en nuestro enlace es posible que tengas que desplazarte hacia abajo en la página, o ir a la siguiente de la página en la búsqueda o volver a nuestro sitio para refinarla. ¡La paciencia es la madre de la ciencia!• ¿Es correcto el descuento?Los enlaces que te ofrecemos se generan de manera totalmente automática de manera que es posible que alguna url no fuese correcta.• Un descuento no siempre es una gangaQue un producto tenga un descuento no quiere decir que no pueda encontrarse más barato en otro sitio. Si no encuentras nada que te convenza al precio que buscas no dejes de mirar en nuestro sitio por otras ofertas y descuentos.• ¿Es un comerciante externo?Como sabes, Amazon dispone de un Marketplace el que otras tiendas pueden vender sus productos. En caso de que la venta no se realizase directamente en Amazon.es podría ser que no todo fuese tan sencillo con los envíos y devoluciones.• Consigue el envío gratuitoA veces algo tan sencillo como comprar un producto que cueste poco te puede ahorrar los gastos de envío.Amazon.es tiene unas tarifas de envío bastante razonables, pero aún así, como ahorrador concienciado querrás siempre evitártelas. Ten encuenta que las tarifas de envío de Amazon.es dependen mucho de la sección en la que compras, el dinero que te has gastado y si tienes Amazon Premium o no. Nuestro consejo es que si tu compra no llega la mínimo, gastes un poco más en un CD, o alguna cosa pequeña hasta completar el gasto mínimo. Eso sí, intenta comprar algo que fueses a comprar de todas formas puesto que si no, el ahorro será sólo psicológico.Como ejemplo, actualmente el envío en Amazon.es es gratuito para tus pedidos de la categoría Zapatos y complementos y para calzado y ropa de la categoría Deportes y aire libre, y si haces un pedido de un importe mínimo de 19 € en la compra de libros vendidos y enviados por Amazon.--------------------DEUTSCH--------------------Finden Sie versteckte Rabatte bei Amazon. Discount Finder hilft finden sie besten Angebote bis 90% rabatt.Entdecken Sie versteckte Angebote, Artikel & Rabatte bei der Suche nach Produkten auf Amazon.Jetzt mehr als 75% Rabatt finden!Einfach nach Ihrem Wunschartikel suchen und richtig sparen! Das Rabatt findet alle versteckten Rabatte auf Amazon und zeigt Ihnen diese. Einfach mal ausprobieren, es lohnt sich!

description: IPEVO Whiteboard per Chromebook è specificamente progettato per creare una lavagna interattiva con IPEVO IW2 sul tuo Chromebook. IPEVO Whiteboard for ChromebookAdd Even More Versatility to Your IW2IPEVO Whiteboard for Chromebook is specifically designed for the IPEVO IW2 Wireless Interactive Whiteboard System on your Chromebook, adding versatility to both! Whiteboard allows you to draw or annotate directly onto a blank whiteboard or imported images in order to highlight, emphasize or clarify areas of interest – for education and for business. In addition, by pairing any one of IPEVO’s document cameras with your Chromebook, or by using the device's built-in webcam, you can stream live image from the document camera/webcam to your Chromebook and annotate that live image as well.How does IPEVO Whiteboard for Chromebook work?- IPEVO Whiteboard for Chromebook allows your IW2 to work with Chromebook. Just set up your IW2, open the app, take a minute to calibrate, and you are now ready to use your IW2 with your Chromebook- When your Chromebook is connected to a projector, this setup gives you a projected interactive whiteboard- An easy-to-use annotation toolkit is available in the app. You can import images from your folders or from Google Drive and then draw or annotate on them to emphasize, highlight or clarify key areas of interest using IW2- Or, you can choose to write, draw and annotate directly onto a blank whiteboard - After you're done, you can take snapshots of the annotated images/whiteboards and save them temporarily to the app, or you can export them directly to designated folders or Google Drive for future use or sharingEnjoy quick and simple annotation features- Draw freely with the Pen tools, or choose a straight line or rectangle for highlighting important areas. There are several different colors and sizes to choose from- Time-saving Eraser, Undo, Redo, Copy & Paste, and Delete functionsBenefit from effortless image management- Take snapshots and save the annotated images/whiteboards to the app, or export the annotated whiteboards directly to your designated folders or Google Drive for future use, archiving, and reference- One-tap easy access to Review Mode lets you view and manage snapshots saved to the app. From there, you can export them to other folders for archiving- Choose from two file formats – JPG and PDF – when exporting annotated images/whiteboards or saved snapshots Don't have IW2? No worries. You can still use IPEVO Whiteboard for Chromebook with a computer mouse or an IPEVO document camera - IPEVO Whiteboard for Chromebook can also be used with a computer mouse. You’ll enjoy the same features you would with an IW2- Using Whiteboard with an IPEVO document camera is another option. Stream a live image from the document camera to your Chromebook, then draw or annotate on that live image using Whiteboard's annotation toolkit - Or, choose Chromebook's built-in webcam to stream a live image to your Chromebook and draw or annotate onto the live image just as you would with the live stream from an IPEVO document camera- Annotated live images can also be saved as snapshots in the app, or exported to your designated folders or to Google Drive

description: Passione per la fotografia ai sali d'argento Analogica.it nasce come Forum dedicato alla condivisione e divulgazione delle conoscenze legate alle tecniche di camera oscura, ossia a tutte quelle pratiche e metodologie che ruotano attorno al mondo della fotografia tradizionale dai più conosciuta come “fotografia analogica” o “fotografia chimica“.  Il termine stesso “fotografia analogica” è relativamente giovane, nato dopo l’avvento del digitale che ha di fatto generato la separazione, spesso solo ideologica, tra pixel ed argento.  Noi siamo convinti, a prescindere dal supporto, che la fotografia sia fotografia; tuttavia coltiviamo ed amiamo le tecniche legate al trattamento degli alogenuri d’argento e proprio per questo amiamo definirci “Appassionati della fotografia ai sali d’argento”.  Il Forum ha riscosso un imprevisto successo, vantando centinaia di iscritti e moltissimi thread di varia natura, sulle più svariate tematiche, dalle tecniche di camera oscura (sviluppo, fissaggio, stampa, … ) agli accessori per camera oscura (timer, ingranditori, marginatori, …), per non parlare delle fotocamere (35mm, medio formato, grande formato), dei supporti (rullini, carte da stampa sia politenate che baritate, … ) e dei prodotti chimici per lo sviluppo e la stampa (rivelatori, arresti, fissaggi, … ).  Abbiamo cosi deciso di ampliare il forum dedicando al mondo della fotografia tradizionale anche un blog, nel quale verranno trattati specifici argomenti su tecniche di camera oscura, tutorial, approfondimenti, segnalazioni, immagini degli utenti ed altro ancora.  Il progetto è in continuo divenire e tutti gli iscritti alla community ne sono partecipi attivamente.
name: analogica.it

description: Scanner di frodi della Polizia di Internet Fraude Scanner: Altijd gewaarschuwd voor online oplichting🛡️Als je het internet gebruikt, wil je niet onverwachts op een onveilige website terechtkomen en slachtoffer worden van online.Bescherm jezelf tegen online gevaren met de Fraude Scanner. Deze extensie waarschuwt je 24/7 voor frauduleuze websites, online oplichters en verdachte linkjes (phishing), zodat jij veilig blijft tijdens het browsen en online winkelen.De voordelen:Extra veilig: Met onze extensie ben je altijd beschermd tegen online fraude. Makkelijk in gebruik: Zie in één oogopslag of een website te vertrouwen is. Privacy eerst: We respecteren je privacy. We weten niet wie je bent en dat willen we ook zo houden. Nederlands product: Ontwikkeld in Nederland, met kennis van lokale bedreigingen.Altijd gratis: Je kunt de extensie gratis gebruiken en je online veiligheid verhogen.Hoe het werkt:Wij doen het werk: Nieuwe verdachte websites worden binnen 4 minuten toegevoegd aan onze database.Automatische bescherming: Terwijl je online bent, scant de extensie automatisch de websites die je bezoekt.Duidelijke signalen: Direct veilig via onze kleurcodes. Groene, gele en rode kleuren laten je snel zien of een website veilig is.Community feedback: Andere gebruikers delen hun ervaringen. Zo helpen we elkaar om veilig te blijven.Meld verdachte websitesMet onze rapportagefunctie in de extensie, kun je snel onveilige websites aan ons doorgeven.Makkelijk melden: Een verdachte site gespot? Meld het in enkele seconden via onze rapportagefunctie en laat ons het zware werk doen.Voor iedereen: Jouw melding helpt andere gebruikers. Zo maken we samen het internet veiliger.Altijd een update: Na je melding houden we je op de hoogte. Je krijgt feedback over de status van je melding en eventuele acties die zijn ondernomen.Ontdek onze community:Praat en leer: Kom in contact met andere gebruikers die hun ervaringen, tips en waarschuwingen over online fraude delen. Help mee: Draag actief bij aan discussies, geef feedback op meldingen en help mee met het identificeren van nieuwe online bedreigingen.Snel antwoord: Via de community krijg je snel hulp of tips als je een vraag hebt over online oplichting.Veelgestelde vragen:Is Internet Politie onderdeel van de Nationale Politie?Nee, we maken geen deel uit van de Nationale Politie, maar we delen wel hetzelfde doel: zoveel mogelijk mensen online beschermen.Heb ik deze extensie  nodig als ik al een virusscanner gebruik?Hoewel virusscanners erg belangrijk zijn, bieden ze geen bescherming tegen online oplichting. Hier komt Internet Politie van pas met onze online Fraude Scanner.Hoe verdient Internet Politie geld als de extensie gratis is?De basisversie van de Fraude Scanner is volledig gratis. Om de kosten te dekken, vergaart Internet Politie inkomsten door een premium abonnement aan te bieden.Wat doet Internet Politie met mijn gegevens en privacy?Jouw privacy is onze prioriteit. Wij koppelen daarom geen data aan personen. Zo blijf je volledig anoniem. Onze focus ligt op het beschermen van jouw online ervaring, niet op het verzamelen van je gegevens.Samen tegen online fraude.Download nu de Fraude Scanner extensie en draag bij aan een veiliger internet voor iedereen. Door de Fraude Scanner extensie te gebruiken verklaar je je akkoord met de algemene voorwaarden van Internet Politie. (https://internetpolitie.nl/algemene-voorwaarden/)Bezoek onze website voor meer informatie over de Fraude Scanner van Internet Politie: https://internetpolitie.nl/
name: Scanner di frodi della Polizia di Internet

description: How can revision and self-assessment be made more engaging, easier and intuitive ? Educational Syllabus for High Schools in CBSE, NCERT, ICSE, IGCSE includes subject like Math, Physics, Chemistry, Biology, Geography, History, Economics, Computer and English. Each day new content is being provided by students as well as teachers from reputed institutes. Apart from just learning, you can also Quiz yourself on the subject as per the syllabus and see how well you know the subject. So it helps as a revision tool for you even during your exams / tests. description: Modalità oscura: tema scuro classico per il Web. Cambia qualsiasi sito web: tema scuro per Instagram, Youtube, Facebook, Google… modalità oscura: il lettore oscuro per Chrome metterà il tema scuro su tutti i siti Web, adatto a chi lavora di notte e il lettore oscuro per le notizie online o la lettura di libri.Applica tutti i siti Web nel browser in modalità oscura ed escludi qualsiasi dominio dal tema nero per una migliore esperienza. È possibile creare il proprio tema personalizzato con qualsiasi colore si desideri.Modalità oscura per i social network: il tema scuro per Instagram, Twitter, Twitch, YouTube e i siti mainstream e tutti gli altri siti Web saranno tutti coperti di colori neri.Se il sito Web ha un tema scuro integrato, puoi controllarlo direttamente dalla modalità notturna e, in caso contrario (come Gmail, Google Docs, Office Online, Github e milioni di altri), l'estensione della modalità oscura convertirà i colori per fornirti con modalità oscura uniforme e coerente.Cosa otterrai dall'estensione della modalità oscura:- Attiva/disattiva la modalità oscura manualmente - Fai clic sull'icona dell'estensione per attivare/disattivare la modalità oscura.- Escludi/Includi un sito dalla modalità oscura - Scegli "Modalità oscura" > "Disabilita/Abilita modalità oscura per questo sito"- Personalizza i colori per i siti web - Cambia tutti i colori che desideri.- Programma automatico - Abilitare "Auto ON/OFF" nella sezione.Non è più necessario aprire le impostazioni una per una per diversi siti Web: solo un'app porta il tema nero su tutta la rete.La pagina delle opzioni è ora disponibile! Caratteristiche utili:- Esclusione del sito. Inserisci un indirizzo web corretto per escludere la pagina dall'applicazione del tema nero.- Esclusione pagine. Facoltativamente, aggiungi i domini che non desideri applicare al tema nero.- Cambia tema. Crea il tuo tema personalizzato! Salvalo, rinominalo e applicalo in qualsiasi momento.Basta installare un'estensione per abilitare la modalità oscura per Chrome.Turno di notteAttiva la modalità Night Shift per invertire la normale luce dello schermo in un tono più caldo, evitando così danni agli occhi. Puoi attivare e disattivare lo strumento con un solo clic quando ne hai bisogno.Il turno di notte e l'estensione del lettore scuro spostano automaticamente i colori del contenuto del browser all'estremità più calda dello spettro dei colori dopo il tramonto.Lettore oscuroDark Reader inverte i colori brillanti, rendendoli ad alto contrasto e facili da leggere di notte. La modalità oscura metterà il tema scuro su tutti i siti Web, adatto a chi lavora di notte e lettore oscuro per notizie online o lettura di libri.L'estensione Super Dark Mode può oscurare quasi tutti i siti Web, nonché i file locali aperti da Chrome, come i PDF. D'ora in poi, i tuoi occhi possono essere rilassati durante la navigazione sul Web sullo schermo di notte.Modalità oscura di Youtube o tema scuro di YoutubeL'estensione Tema scuro per YouTube converte il tema di YouTube in un tema blu/antracite scuro altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Youtube Dark Reader è basata sul tema YouTube predefinito (tema scuro nativo), quindi è molto leggera rispetto all'utilizzo di temi iniettati dalle estensioni Stylish o Stylus.Modalità oscura di Instagram o tema scuro di InstagramL'estensione Instagram Dark Mode converte il tema Instagram in un tema carbone scuro/blu altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Instagram Dark Reader è basata sul tema predefinito di Instagram. Tema scuro di InstagramModalità oscura di Facebook o tema scuro di FacebookL'estensione FB Dark Mode converte il tema di Facebook in un tema antracite scuro/blu altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Facebook Dark Reader è basata sul tema predefinito di Instagram. Tema scuro di FacebookModalità oscura Github o tema scuro GithubL'estensione Github Dark Mode converte il tema Instagram in un tema carbone scuro/blu altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Github Dark Reader è basata sul tema predefinito di Instagram. Tema scuro GithubModalità oscura di Twitter o tema scuro di TwitterL'estensione Twitter Dark Mode converte il tema Twitter in un tema carbone scuro/blu altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Twitter Dark Reader si basa sul tema predefinito di Twitter. Tema scuro di TwitterModalità oscura di Google Documenti e tema scuro di Google DocumentiAttiva la modalità oscura per Google Documenti con un clic tramite questa estensione.Utilizzare una modalità oscura per Google Documenti?L'estensione Dark Mode di Google Docs converte il tema di Google Docs in un tema antracite scuro/blu altamente personalizzabile. L'estensione Google Docs Dark Reader si basa sul tema predefinito di Google Documenti. Tema scuro di Google DocumentiScarica ora la modalità oscura nel tuo browser web! Funzionalità Dark Mode per Google, YouTube, Facebook e molti altri siti Web: scaricala ora e mantieni gli occhi rilassati nelle ore buie!Modalità oscura VK o tema scuro VkTema scuro classico per Vkontakte. Passa VK alla modalità oscura e torna indietro con un clic. Tema scuro VKontakte protegge gli occhi. Elimina il carico di notte, sostituendo lo schermo bianco con un classico tema scuro.Twitch modalità oscura o tema scuro TwitchTwitch dark mode tema scuro nativo altamente personalizzabile per twitch.tv (piattaforma per giocatori). Il tema scuro di Twitch è un tema scuro nativo per la piattaforma di gioco twitch.tv che utilizza il tema scuro integrato per attivare e disattivare la modalità oscura.Modalità oscura per TikTokTema scuro per TikTok. Cambia facilmente la modalità del sito TikTok in scuro o chiaro con un clic.Sentiti libero di fare qualsiasi domanda e lasciare commenti per Dark Theme.

description: WorkOnIT - Your Personal Life Coach in Your Pocket.  Define goals, get coaching, track your progress and invite your friends and… WorkOnIT - Your Personal Life Coach in Your Pocket.  Define goals, get coaching, track your progress and invite your friends and family to help and follow along with you.  Push messaging between you and your followers means you can share messages and photos and get immediately notified without having to open the app.WorkOnIT is also available in an Enterprise Edition for use within a single organization with customized goals, coaching and backend tools to manage and track usage. Visit our support site to learn how you can have a customized WorkOnIT in your organization.WorkOnIT helps you to define your goals, share them with others, and provides coaching advice on how to work better to achieve them.WorkOnIT is the only app providing specific coaching advice to help you in your quest to achieve more. Our WikiCoach system provides a database of coaching information from our own professional coaches, with hand selected links, and auto generated feeds to keep you informed and on track. Whether your goal is business focused, such as asking for feedback, delegating, or selling better, or personal such as reducing stress, eating healthy, or learning to play guitar, we have the coaching advice you need. Our database is growing each day and is community supported, just like Wikipedia, so we allow you to share your advice with others.Sophisticated push messaging keeps you informed when your goal followers are active in helping you. You can even send out a push to your followers to ask them for help and advice.Features:• Defining – Goal creation based on the SMART goal system (Specific, Measurable, Attainable, Relevant, Time-Bound).  We have over 100 goals you can choose from or create your own unique goals!• Tracking – Keep track of the progress you are making towards your goal, frequency of activity and percentage done.• Sharing – Get help from people around you by inviting them to follow you and give you encouragement and advice through comments, star ratings, and reward “medals”.• Coaching – Our WikiCoach database of coaching advice for many of the most common business and personal goals to help you understand how to achieve your goal.• Push Messaging – Integrated push messaging helps keep you informed of your activity with those supporting you. No need to check if you have new advice or words of encouragement, the app takes care of notifying you.In-APP Purchases Available to Extend the Functionality of WorkOnIT to do even More• Add pictures to your comments.  We say "a picture is worth a thousand words" and this add-on allows you to post pictures in your comments to share also with your followers.  It is a great way to visualize your accomplishments and inspire those you are helping to achieve their goals.• Add actions to your goals.  This add-on allows you to create steps within your goal.  Think of actions as milestones along the way to accomplishing your goal.  Each action has a separate due date and an automatic reminder.  You can set as many steps along the way to achieving your goal as you like and your actions are shared with the people you are following.  Your followers will get notifications when you create an action and when it has been completed, helping them to follow your progress towards your goal.
name: WorkOnIT

For all uses of this name, use this The My Hero Academia Boku No to show love ♥.My Hero Academia (僕のヒーローアカデミア Boku no Hīrō Akademia?) is a Japanese superhero manga series written and illustrated by Kōhei Horikoshi. It has been serialized in Weekly Shōnen Jump since July 2014 and 12 volumes have been collected in tankōbon format. The series has been licensed for English-language release by Viz Media, and began serialization in their weekly digital manga anthology Weekly Shonen Jump on February 9, 2015. The story follows Izuku Midoriya, a boy born without superpowers in a world where they are the norm, but who still dreams of becoming a superhero himself, and is scouted by the world's greatest hero who shares his powers with Izuku after recognizing his value and enrolls him in a high school for heroes in training. The manga was adapted into an anime television series; the first season aired from April 3 to June 26, 2016,and a second season premiered on April 1, 2017.
